s & Records\"/>\n* [[Serie A Italian Footballer of the Year]]: 1998, 2008<ref name=\"Alessandro Del Piero: Awards & Records\"/>\n* Serie A-Top assist provider: [[1999\u20132000 Serie A|1999\u20132000]]<ref name=\"Serie A 1999/2000\"/>\n* [[Oscar del Calcio|Oscar AIC-Serie A Fan Award]]: 2001, 2008<ref name=\"Alessandro Del Piero: Awards & Records\"/>\n* [[FIFA 100]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/2374252/Pele-open-to-ridicule-over-top-hundred.html|title=Pele open to ridicule over top hundred|website=telegraph.co.uk|publisher=The Telegraph|author1=Christopher Davies|date=5 March 2004|accessdate=13 April 2015}}</ref>\n* [[UEFA Golden Jubilee Poll]]: Top 50 1954\u20132004, Top 250 1994\u20132003<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/newsfiles/171606.pdf|title=Zinedine Zidane voted top player by fans|website=UEFA.com|accessdate=24 July 2014}}</ref>\n* [[Coppa Italia]]-Top scorer: [[2005\u201306 Coppa Italia|2005\u201306]] (5 goals)<ref name=\"Alessandro Del Piero: Awards & Records\"/>\n* Giuseppe Prisco National Award: 2006<ref>{{cite news|url=http://bologna.repubblica.it/dettaglio-news/la-mia-strega-un-po-pinguino-vestita-da-veglione-ma-brucera/1410627|title=CALCIO, PREMIO PRISCO A SENSI, DEL PIERO E GIAMPAOLO|newspaper=La Repubblica|language=Italian|date=5 April 2006|accessdate=12 January 2016}}</ref>\n* USSI Prize-Italian sportsman of the year: 2006<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.conipiemonte.net/documentazione/comunicati/070202_delpiero.htm |title=Notizie |publisher=Conipiemonte.net |language=Italian |date= |accessdate=22 July 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070607/http://www.conipiemonte.net/documentazione/comunicati/070202_delpiero.htm |archive-date=4 March 2016 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n* Special Prize Gentleman Silver Cup: 2006<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/Altro_Calcio/Primo_Piano/2006/05_Maggio/08/gentelman.shtml|title=Premio Gentleman: riconoscimenti a Del Piero e Maldini|newspaper=La Gazzetta dello Sport|language=Italian|date=8 May 2006|accessdate=12 January 2016}}</ref>\n* San Siro Gentleman Award Serie A: 2006<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.premiogentleman.it/albo-doro/milano-2006/|title=Milano 2006 \u2013 Premio Gentleman|publisher=Premio Gentleman|language=Italian|accessdate=12 January 2016}}</ref>\n* [[Serie B|Serie B-Top scorer]]: [[2006\u201307 Serie B#Top goalscorers|2006\u201307]] (20 goals)<ref name=\"Alessandro Del Piero: Awards & Records\"/>\n* [[Golden Foot award|Golden Foot Award]]: 2007<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goldenfoot.com/en/legends.html |title=Golden Foot Legends |website=goldenfoot.com |accessdate=27 March 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416024500/http://www.goldenfoot.com/en/legends.html |archivedate=16 April 2015 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://archiviostorico.gazzetta.it/2007/settembre/04/Ale_vince_Golden_Foot_2007_ga_10_070904042.shtml|title=Ale vince il Golden Foot 2007 Premiato dal principe Alberto|newspaper=La Gazzetta dello Sport|language=Italian|date=4 September 2007|accessdate=13 May 2015}}</ref>\n* Telegatto-Best Sportsman: 2007<ref>{{cite news|url=http://ricerca.gelocal.it/nuovavenezia/archivio/nuovavenezia/2007/01/26/VT1VM_VT100.html|title=Telegatti, vince anche Fiorello|newspaper=La Repubblica|language=Italian|date=26 January 2007|accessdate=12 January 2016}}</ref>\n* [[Association of Football Statisticians|ASF]] Top-100 Players of All-Time \u2013 #60: 2007<ref name=\"AFS Top-100 Players of All-Time\"/>\n* [[Capocannoniere|Serie A-Top scorer]]: [[2007\u201308 Serie A#Top goalscorers|2007\u201308]] (21 goals)<ref name=\"Alessandro Del Piero: Awards & Records\"/>\n* [[Oscar del Calcio#Serie A Goalscorer of the Year|Oscar AIC-Top scorer]]: [[2007\u201308 Serie A#Top goalscorers|2008]]<ref name=\"Alessandro Del Piero: Awards & Records\"/>\n* [[Premio Nazionale Carriera Esemplare \"Gaetano Scirea\"]]: 2008<ref name=\"Premio Nazionale Carriera Esemplare Gaetano Scirea: Alba d'Oro\"/>\n* [[Pallone d'Argento]]: 2008\u201309<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ussi.it/2016/a-florenzi-il-pallone-dargento-coppa-giaime-fiumano/|title=A Florenzi il \"Pallone d\u2019Argento\" Coppa Giaim\u00e8 Fiumano|publisher=ussi.it|language=Italian|date=8 May 2016|accessdate=18 May 2016}}</ref>\n* International Award for Sport and Civility-Ambassador of Sports: 2009<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.tuttosport.com/calcio/serie_a/juventus/2009/11/12-45362/Premio+Internazionale+Sport+Civilt%C3%A0+ad+Alessandro+Del+Piero|title=Premio Internazionale Sport Civilt\u00e0 ad Alessandro Del Piero|newspaper=Tuttosport|language=Italian|date=12 November 2009|accessdate=12 January 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112645/http://www.tuttosport.com/calcio/serie_a/juventus/2009/11/12-45362/Premio+Internazionale+Sport+Civilt%C3%A0+ad+Alessandro+Del+Piero|archive-date=4 March 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* Sportsman of the Year Golden Award: 2010<ref name=\"Alessandro Del Piero: Awards & Records\"/>\n* [[Globe Soccer Awards|Globe Soccer Career Award]]: 2011<ref name=\"Alessandro Del Piero: Awards & Records\"/><ref name=GSA>{{cite web|url=http://www.globesoccer.com/awards/walloffame/|title=Wall of Fame|publisher=Globe Soccer.com|accessdate=28 December 2015}}</ref>\n* Novara Fair Play Award: 2011<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.calciomercato.com/altre-notizie/premio-fair-play-novara-vince-del-piero-652117|title=Premio Fair Play Novara: vince Del Piero &#124; Altre notizie|publisher=Calciomercato.com|language=Italian|date=4 February 2014}}</ref>\n* [[Oscar del Calcio#Lifetime Achievement Award|Oscar AIC-Award to Career]] 2011<ref name=\"Alessandro Del Piero: Awards & Records\"/>\n* A-League goal of the season: 2012\u201313<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/news-display/del-piero-rocket-voted-goal-of-the-season/66382 |title=Del Piero rocket voted goal of the season \u2013 Football Australia 2013 |publisher=Footballaustralia.com.au |date= |accessdate=22 July 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129030453/http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/news-display/del-piero-rocket-voted-goal-of-the-season/66382 |archivedate=29 November 2014  }}</ref>\n* [[List of Sydney FC records and statistics#Top goalscorers|Sydney FC Golden Boot]]: [[2012\u201313 Sydney FC season#Goal scorers|2013]],<ref name=\"footballaustralia2\"/> [[2013\u201314 Sydney FC season#Goal scorers|2014]]<ref name=\"Sydney FC Golden Boot\"/>\n* [[PFA Footballer of the Year Awards#A-League Team of the Season|PFA Team of the Season]]: [[PFA Footballer of the Year Awards#2012\u201313|2013]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/news-display/pfa-team-of-the-season-named/66078 |title=PFA Team of the Season named \u2013 Football Australia 2013 |publisher=Footballaustralia.com.au |date= |accessdate=22 July 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129030502/http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/news-display/pfa-team-of-the-season-named/66078 |archivedate=29 November 2014  }}</ref>\n* Sydney FC Player of the Year Award: 2013<ref name=\"footballaustralia2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/sydneyfc/news-display/alessandro-del-piero-wins-sydney-fc-player-of-the-year-award/64882|title=Alessandro Del Piero Wins Sydney FC Player of the Year Award \u2013 Sydney FC \u2013 Sydney FC 2014|publisher=Footballaustralia.com.au|accessdate=12 January 2016}}</ref>\n* Sydney FC Members Award: 2013<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.footballaustralia.com.au/sydneyfc/videos/all/Alessandro-Del-Piero-Named-Members-Player-of-the-Year/8089/1 |title=Videos &#124; Sydney FC |publisher=Footballaustralia.com.au |date=2 October 2012}}</ref>\n* [[2014 A-League All Stars Game|A-League All Stars Game: 2014]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/local/photos/2014/08/04/4060479.htm|title=Del Piero excited for All Stars game and beyond|publisher=ABC.net|author1=Justin Huntsdale|date=4 August 2014|a